{"tid":1743050,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"11月24日，十八區長者愛心慈善派米！","createTime":"2019-11-21T04:48:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T12:12:55.000Z","uid":42093,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ca026454429806991415f0fc422e4ee71ec3d25c","tid":1743050,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:48:31.000Z","msg":"近日既社會氣氛不穩令各位老友記都好唔開心，<br />\n如果我地發起，一個十八區長者愛心慈善派米，為長者送暖<br />\n係十一月二十四日上午7 時30 分至晚上10 時30 分，不定時上門派米，<br />\n安坐家中，只要年滿60歲，親身出示身份證就會有白米一包，<br />\n相信一班老友記都會留係屋企，安心等我地既白米送到，<br />\n確定佢地全日安坐家中，為呢一日帶黎新既意義。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29013cbbe5b99a43b0681d66375acbf9629a4e61","tid":1743050,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:49:10.000Z","msg":"自推，為長者送暖你我有責"},{"pid":"57d97227aac47c046542d0c89a59400075fb3084","tid":1743050,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"自推，為長者送暖你我有責"},{"pid":"170bd51f7d76651bda27f1b7cfcb32c5e4c2cfff","tid":1743050,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"自推，為長者送暖你我有責"},{"pid":"8bc985c4ca7ef460a2e1b79d388a9ee68d9f43f7","tid":1743050,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"文宣, 要貼出黎"},{"pid":"6b95b274cd78a9fd73a5dc5440a009eafb5a5cd2","tid":1743050,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bc985c4ca7ef460a2e1b79d388a9ee68d9f43f7","tid":1743050,"uid":92347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:51:50.000Z","msg":"文宣, 要貼出黎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:53:29.000Z","msg":"長者有著數，長者要知道"},{"pid":"2c023c266e79d069ec8985419185cf1e9ea2c867","tid":1743050,"uid":42093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T04:54:54.000Z","msg":"自推，為長者送暖你我有責"},{"pid":"8a558bab8b74f8b0fc3e40cbf4f0fe7adf1eb525","tid":1743050,"uid":51598,"like":0,"d